### Test Notification Service API

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Create Notification Template
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "email",
  "title": "Welcome to our app",
  "body": "Thank you for joining us! We're excited to have you on board.",
  "data": {
    "priority": "high",
    "category": "welcome"
  }
}

### Get All Templates
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/templates

### Create User Notification
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notification_id": "{{template_id}}"
}

### Get User Notifications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/notifications?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Unread Count
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/notifications/unread-count

### Mark Notifications as Read
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/notifications/read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notification_ids": ["{{notification_id}}"]
}

### Send Bulk Notifications
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/templates/{{template_id}}/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_ids": [
    "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
    "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001",
    "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002"
  ]
}

### Update Template
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/templates/{{template_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Welcome Message",
  "body": "Welcome to our amazing app! We're thrilled to have you here."
}

### Delete User Notification
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/notifications/{{notification_id}}

### Delete Template
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/templates/{{template_id}}
